         <abstract id="aspace_7c4bd2a161242f25f19141bbe937b869">The materials consist of photographs of various scenes of Yale and New Haven buildings and grounds. Subjects include interior views of classrooms, the gymnasium, and the library; exterior views of fraternities; and photographs of Grove Street Cemetery, as well as other prominent Yale and New Haven, Connecticut landmarks.</abstract>
